71
00:08:13,050 --> 00:08:16,240
In the past, Tang Clan reached its zenith.

72
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:19,190
No one was a match for us.

73
00:08:19,190 --> 00:08:21,600
However, with the fame growing,

74
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:24,940
