more red tape were created.

75
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:27,960
The outer disciples couldn’t practice
the highest skills.

76
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:30,490
The inner disciples are not qualified enough.

77
00:08:30,490 --> 00:08:34,110
