many secret scriptures lose.

78
00:08:34,110 --> 00:08:39,090
In this way, Tang Clan couldn’t
escape its fate of falling.

79
00:08:39,910 --> 00:08:42,390
Only the survival of the fittest, being eclectic,

80
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:45,420
